    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"break\" doesn't really work though. If there's nothing underneath the mask, what am i even taking a break from? It's like... if the person who was actually living this life is gone, then this version of me is just a ghost. A ghost that has to keep paying bills and pretending to be human. It feels so pointless to keep the charade going when the real me is already dead or just... gone.",
